# Built installer output - never commit binaries to the repo.
dist/

# Branding placeholders. Real artwork is supplied per-build and is not
# tracked here so designers can iterate without polluting git history.
# If you decide to commit your final branding assets, remove the lines
# below or add a forced negation rule such as `!assets/wizard-side.bmp`.
assets/*.bmp
assets/*.ico

# Inno Setup compiler intermediates (rare, but possible if /O is misused).
*.iss.bak
*.iss~

# OS clutter.
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
